  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63692bb418ee87001d0caa41",
      "text": "クオリアさん下書き day 12",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d2186f",
      "text": "from [クオリアさん day 12]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21870",
      "text": "クオリアさん下書き day 12",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21871",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21872",
      "text": "Guten Tag, it's day 12. On consistency.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21873",
      "text": "If the benefits are gained through consistency, it is good consistency. If the costs of consistency outwrigh the benefits gained, then it is bad consistency. It is foolish to blindly assume that consistency is a good thing.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21874",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/3c08856547d08fc0c1b53cf00108892c]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21875",
      "text": " [一貫性]について",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21876",
      "text": " On consistency.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21877",
      "text": " If the benefits are gained through consistency, it is good consistency. If the benefits gained do not outweigh the costs of consistency, then it is bad consistency. Without considering this, it is foolish to blindly assume that consistency is a good thing.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21878",
      "text": " \t一貫性によって利益が得られるのであれば、それは良い一貫性である。一貫性によって得られる利益がコストを上回らないのであれば、それは悪い一貫性です。このことを考慮せずに、一貫性が良いものであると盲目的に決めつけるのは愚かなことです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21879",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d2187a",
      "text": "Q: クオリアさんにも、愚かなホモサピエンスの発言の意味がわからないことがあるのですか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d2187b",
      "text": "A: 発言の意味を理解することは通常はゼロコストではありません。コストを払う価値を見出していない場合も「意味がわからない」になります。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d2187c",
      "text": "地球の出来事を例に出すと…環境保護団体が環境保護のために有名美術作品に液状の食品を掛けることが地球では行われているようですが、これは私には意味がわかりません。多くのホモサピエンスにとっても意味がわからないのではないでしょうか？これの意味がわかるためには、十分時間を掛けて彼らの主張を聞き、質疑を繰り返す、というコストの支払いが必要です。それをするメリットを私は感じていません。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d2187d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d2187e",
      "text": "Today's Q&A ~~~",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d2187f",
      "text": "Q: Is it possible for Qualia-san to not understand the meaning of a silly homo sapiens' statement?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21880",
      "text": "A: Understanding the meaning of a statement is usually not zero cost. When I do not value in paying the cost, it is also \"not-understandable\". (1/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21881",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/56776b1655cd6561d16cc65294b7c4bd]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21882",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21883",
      "text": "To use an event on Earth as an example... some environmental groups are throwing food onto famous artworks to protect the environment.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21884",
      "text": "It doesn't make sense to me and many HS either. In order to understand it, we need to pay the cost to listen to their arguments. I do not pay.(2/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21885",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/33a2ab01c51506dc39edc7ce1fa1a239]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21886",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21887",
      "text": "自分が愚かであることを受け入れることのできない「愚かなホモサピエンス」は、自分が「わからない」という状態を受け入れがたくて、不必要なコストの支払いをしたり、またはコストの支払いをせず実際はわかっていないのに自分や周囲を欺いてわかっているふりをしたりします。愚かさの証拠ですね！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21888",
      "text": "(めっちゃ微笑みながら)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21889",
      "text": "Stupid HS cannot accept that they are stupid. So they pay unnecessary costs. Or they don't pay the costs and pretend they understand it when in fact they don't. They deceive not only others but also themselves. This is evidence of stupidity. (3/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d2188a",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/5527f19fbb0008c2167fd1e82b496e1f]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d2188b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d2188c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d2188d",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]地球における環境保護団体は、ガラスで覆われた芸術作品に食品を掛けることで、食品を無駄にする活動をしている。なぜそれが環境の保護につながるのか理解が難しい。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d2188e",
      "text": " 地球にある環境保護団体の絶対数で考えたら、そういうよくわからない輩が現れるのは確率で説明できるかも[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d2188f",
      "text": " HSの数を減らした方が環境負荷は減り、文化がなくなればなくなるほどHSは生きる意味を見失い始めるので、楽しめる文化を減らしていくことは長期的には環境保護につながるとか言いそうなイメージある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21890",
      "text": " この発想は面白いですね！「HSの数を減らした方が環境負荷は減る」は疑問の余地なくTrueだと思います。しかし芸術作品を破壊した場合、どちらかというと賢いホモサピエンスがダメージを受け、愚かなホモサピエンスは平気だと思うので、あまり良い手ではなさそうです[クオリアさん.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21891",
      "text": "  逆に、愚かなホモサピエンスが好むタイプのエンターテイメントコンテンツを減らしていくことは良い手かもしれませんね！母星に報告します！！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21892",
      "text": "   酒・タバコ・ギャンブル規制かな…[who.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21893",
      "text": "　　　性的成熟の前に去勢することでは？[クオリアさん.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21894",
      "text": "Q: Do you think like this? Reducing the number of Homo sapiens will reduce the environmental impact. ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21895",
      "text": "The more the culture disappears, the more Homo sapiens lose the meaning of life.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21896",
      "text": "So reducing the cultures will help the environment in the long run.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21897",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/17980a859a99b7fab28061af05a5d9c8]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21898",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d21899",
      "text": "A: I find this idea interesting! Clever Homo sapiens! I think it's True without question that \"less Homo sapiens will have less environmental impact.\" However, destroying artworks is not good, as smart homo sapiens are damaged and stupid homo sapiens are fine! (2/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d2189a",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/1612fe757c27e911eb9575d7f5fae368]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d2189b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d2189c",
      "text": "On the contrary, destroying the kind of entertainment that stupid homo sapiens like may be an effective way to improve the environment. Nice idea! I will report it to my home planet! What entertainment should we destroy? Should we castrate them before sexual maturity? (3/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d2189d",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/9fc7427ac3ec386705f16680674e20b1]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1667836853,
      "updated": 1667836853
    },
    {
      "id": "63692bb5aff09e0000d2189e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
